channel.title: Rooaarr! -My new free dubstep song :)
channel.description:
Download now!-> [url]https://kiwi6.com/file/90w82yk1h9[/url] youtube link-> [url]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s60AAq8uu_I[/url]
Don't usually post a new thread for one of my songs, but I couldn't help myself. My long awaited new song- Roooaaarrr! Spent many sleepless nights on this, and It feels like my ear drums are burnt out. Every sound is custom made like always, and there's 10 different basses alone in this song. A lot of the percussion was made with my beatboxing skillz, just a fun fact. Hope everybody who listens to this doesn't have crappy speakers and enjoys it :wink:
